category: Devel Lua
requires: lua
sdesc: "Extended Lua C/C++ code generator"
ldesc: "tolua++ is an extended version of tolua, a tool to integrate 
C/C++ code with Lua. tolua++ includes new features oriented to c++ such 
as:

* Support for std::string as a basic type                                     
* Support for class templates

As well as other features and bugfixes."
